data.title: Expertise about the Free Territory & Free Port of Trieste
data.meta_description: Video and documents of the press conference of the International Provisional Representative of the Free Territory of Trieste - I.P.R. F.T.T. about the status of the Italian temporary civil administration of the Free Territory & international Free Port of Trieste.
data.meta_site_name: Sito ufficiale del Movimento Trieste Libera
data.text:
I.P.R. F.T.T. - press conference about the verification of

the special trusteeship over the Free Territory & Free Port of Trieste

We publish the video of the press conference held by the I.P.R. F.T.T. â International Provisional Representative of the Free Territory of Trieste regarding the status of the Italian temporary civil administration of the Free Territory & international Free Port of Trieste as well as the link to Expertise SG/2016/LC/M-IV.1, in English and in Italian: Monitoring of the Italian administration of the Free Territory and international Free Port of Trieste â FALSIFICATION OF THE TREATIES AND SIMULATION OF SOVEREIGNTY in Italian administrative and judicial acts: judgments TAR FVG No. 400/2013 and No. 530/2013 and the documents related or similar to them.

In a few days, the Free Trieste Movement is providing specific forms to make it easier sending communications to the administrative bodies that have already been informed about the status of Trieste (the full list is published on the website of the International Provisional Representative of State).
